flowchart LR
    A[Teaching episode<br/>task, failure mode, extracted lesson]
    B[Protocol artifact<br/>externalized reusable procedure]
    C[Benchmark packet<br/>baseline and taught conditions]
    D[Retained runs<br/>outputs, worksheets, score summaries]
    E[Scored comparison<br/>within-model uplift and failure analysis]
    F[Synthesis memo<br/>cross-run interpretation and next gate]

    A --> B --> C --> D --> E --> F

    G[Teaching means explicit procedural structure,<br/>not one-off prompt improvement]
    H[Retained outputs enable later audit,<br/>review, and manuscript traceability]

    B -.-> G
    D -.-> H
